{"tid":1289220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第四位戰友：「香港人需要的是革命。」","createTime":"2019-07-06T04:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T04:11:42.000Z","uid":125349,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a198657c835acb3d7f5fff79ffe9f47ab1b1aa44","tid":1289220,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:09:18.000Z","msg":"本土新聞 <br />\n編按：香港傳媒絕大部份封殺麥女士的遺言，就算僅有網媒報道遺言，卻選擇性地將「香港需要的是革命」一句刪去。由於《本土新聞》編輯採信《立場新聞》引述死者朋友所稱，「覺得佢想將遺願話俾人聽」，故此將得到的死者遺言全文照錄。<br />\n<br />\n華文媒體中，截至七月五日下午兩時，編輯只發現台灣的《自由時報》、《台灣英文新聞》、《新頭殼》與本報有報道麥女士的「香港需要的是革命」一句。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2364346950448439&amp;id=1487928594756950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2364346950448439%26id%3D1487928594756950&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=3a4eece6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2364346950448439&amp;id=1487928594756950</a>"},{"pid":"b95d5dbd7a6a2b6c565bacb33d72f778e9e4d8cd","tid":1289220,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}